headline: Nasdaq Announces End-of-Month Open Short Interest Positions in Nasdaq Stocks as of Settlement Date September 30, 2025
summary: NEW YORK, Oct. 09, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- At the end of the settlement date of September 30, 2025, short interest in 3,366 Nasdaq Global MarketSM securities totaled 14,078,324,727 shares compared with 14,035,983,054 shares in 3,341 Global Market issues reported for the prior settlement date of September 15, 2025.
